title: Sackets, Copenhagen, Watertown & IR Advance To Soccer Finals
text:
Sackets, Copenhagen, Watertown & IR Advance To Soccer Finals   14, 2015 at 7:03 AM   14, 2015 at 7:11 AM EDT 
Frontier League soccer playoffs got underway Tuesday with boys' A and D Division semifinals. Sackets Harbor and Copenhagen both advanced in the D Division, while in the A Division, Watertown and Indian River move to the next level. Watch the video for highlights from all four games.
